<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.220850>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Mycterothrips mahvelatensis sp. n. Female: (1) Base of fore wing and scale (left); (2) Head & pronotum; (3) Antenna (right); (4) Mesonotum & metascutum; (5) Tergites II – IV; (6) Tergites VII – X; (7) Sternites V – VII." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/220850/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

